{"name": "django-any-js", "metadata": {"name": "django-any-js", "version": "1.2", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Framework :: Django :: 2.2", "Framework :: Django :: 3.0", "Framework :: Django :: 3.1", "Framework :: Django :: 3.2", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content"], "home_page": "https://edugit.org/AlekSIS/libs/django-any-js", "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["Django"], "summary": "Include JavaScript/CSS libraries with readable template tags", "upload_time": 1701731634}, "documentation": ["# Django Any-JS\n\n## Description\n\nDjango-Any-JS helps you at including any combination of JavaScript/CSS\nURLs in your site, with readable settings and template tags.\n\n## Usage\n\nIn your settings:\n\n```\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\n    ...,\n    \"django_any_js\",\n    ...,\n]\nANY_JS = {\n    \"DataTables\": {\n        \"js_url\": \"/javascript/jquery-datatables/dataTables.bootstrap4.min.js\",\n        \"css_url\": \"/javascript/jquery-datatables/css/dataTables.bootstrap4.min.css\",\n    }\n}\n```\n\nIn your template:\n\n```\n{% load any_js %}\n{% include_js \"DataTables\" %}\n{% include_css \"DataTables\" %}\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "django_any_js.templatetags", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_any_js", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_any_js.templatetags.any_js", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "django_any_js.templatetags.any_js.include_js", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "django_any_js.templatetags.any_js.include_css", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "django_any_js.templatetags.any_js.register", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_any_js.apps", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "django_any_js.apps.DjangoAnyJSConfig", "bases": ["AppConfig"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "django_any_js.apps.DjangoAnyJSConfig.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}]}